  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058550/extras/cc7c783ec79c57efe26764f9ef4684d5.avif?t=1772528875\" width=748 height=896 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is «REWOLBOROUGH»?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a story about a girl named Suzen, who unwillingly became involved in an illegal “<strong>family</strong>” business. Having revealed the disconcerting truth about her past life, the heroine has only one desire - to unravel the sinister web of conspiracy that has covered every corner of this troubled city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058550/extras/e2a6401814c0d02b9cdac405afddde20.avif?t=1772528875\" width=1464 height=1132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To date, <strong>six</strong> chapters of the planned <strong>seven</strong> are available:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Chapter I The Awakening </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Chapter II Nobody Loves You </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Chapter III The Vampiress</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chapter IV The Betrayal</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chapter V Cat and Mouse</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>offline version</strong> and <strong>artworks</strong> are available in the root folder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >REWOLBOROUGH VOL.1\\content</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay tuned for updates.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058550/extras/cc7c783ec79c57efe26764f9ef4684d5.avif?t=1772528875\" width=748 height=896 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is «REWOLBOROUGH»?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a story about a girl named Suzen, who unwillingly became involved in an illegal “<strong>family</strong>” business. Having revealed the disconcerting truth about her past life, the heroine has only one desire - to unravel the sinister web of conspiracy that has covered every corner of this troubled city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058550/extras/e2a6401814c0d02b9cdac405afddde20.avif?t=1772528875\" width=1464 height=1132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To date, <strong>six</strong> chapters of the planned <strong>seven</strong> are available:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Chapter I The Awakening </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Chapter II Nobody Loves You </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Chapter III The Vampiress</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chapter IV The Betrayal</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chapter V Cat and Mouse</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>offline version</strong> and <strong>artworks</strong> are available in the root folder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >REWOLBOROUGH VOL.1\\content</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay tuned for updates.</p>",
